Buat produk baru via form produk:

| Field | Isian |
|-------|-------|
| **Nama** | `Isi Ulang Galon Sumur 19L` |
| **SKU** | `REFILL-ONLY-SUMUR` |
| **Tipe** | `Storable Product (Inventori)` |
| **Metode Pembelian** | `Make to Order` |
| **Dapat Dibeli** | ❌ |
| **Dapat Dijual** | ✅ |
| **Harga Jual** | `7000` (sama dengan galon reguler) |
| **UOM** | `Unit` |

Lalu buat BOM (tanpa galon):

| # | Komponen | Qty | UOM |
|---|----------|-----|-----|
| 1 | Air Baku Sumur | 19 | Liter |
| 2 | Tutup Galon Sumur | 1 | Unit |
| 3 | Tag Galon Sumur | 1 | Unit |

> Tidak ada Galon di BOM karena customer bawa galon sendiri.

### B. Custom Refill (Isi per liter, wadah customer)

| Field | Isian |
|-------|-------|
| **Nama** | `Isi Air Sumur (per Liter)` |
| **SKU** | `REFILL-SUMUR` |
| **Tipe** | `Storable Product (Inventori)` |
| **Metode Pembelian** | `Make to Order` |
| **Dapat Dijual** | ✅ |
| **Harga Jual** | `400` (Rp 400 per liter) |
| **UOM** | `Liter` |

BOM Custom Refill:

| # | Komponen | Qty | UOM |
|---|----------|-----|-----|
| 1 | Air Baku Sumur | 1 | Liter |

> 1 liter output = 1 liter air baku. Tanpa wadah/tutup/segel (wadah milik customer).

