## Checklist Ringkasan

### Produk yang Harus Dibuat

- [ ] Air Baku Sumur (`AIR-BAKU-SUMUR`) — bahan baku, Liter, purchase_ok
- [ ] Tag Galon Sumur (`TAG-SUMUR`) — consumable, Unit, purchase_ok
- [ ] Tutup Galon Sumur (`TUTUP-SUMUR`) — consumable, Unit, purchase_ok
- [ ] Galon Sumur (`AIR_SUMUR`) — storable, Unit, sale_ok, make_to_order

### BOM yang Harus Dibuat

- [ ] BOM Galon Sumur (5 komponen: Galon Flexible + Air + Tutup + Tag)

### Alur Operasional

- [ ] PO bahan baku → Approve → Confirm → Receipt → Stok masuk
- [ ] Manufacturing Order → Confirm → Start → Record → Finish → Galon Sumur tersedia
- [ ] Sales Order → Confirm → Delivery/Pickup → Payment → Done

### Opsional

- [ ] Refill-Only produk + BOM (tanpa galon)
